	desc = "EMPTY FUCK. LOSER. LONER. PIECE OF SHIT. THE WORLD HAS FAILED YOU. You do not deserve salvation; none of this wretched fucking plane does.</br> The Archdevyl Vheslyn rose to wreak destruction 'pon Psydonia, the thunderous Godhead split the earth, a sun-maw of shimmering flame atop a colossal, pallid worm. All the world which witnessed her directly was silenced in an instant; their eyes burnt from their skulls, bodies reduced to ash. All lyfe bathed in ochre-violet flame twisted in corruption. Even the lucky and spared who did not witness the single moment of Her reign were affected; weeping sores and burns 'cross their bodies, a radiance without heat that killed them from inside. They would die, coughing blood from their lungs, as their hair wilted from their heads and their skin fell off in scabs. </br> You have reached the bottom of all things; the final layer to peel back. All reality is suffering. The only way to save this broken world is to destroy it completely. It does not matter whether something will rise from the ashes. Whether their enemies are the followers of Psydon, the Ten, or the Four, their goal is the same. To tear the slaves of Reality from their heavens, to gut their followers upon the altar of death and destruction, and to let this world die in a paroxysm of frenzy and wrath. </br>  </br> The world is ending. The garden is on fire, and you are holding a torch. They will all fall in your wake. You will die. But your death simply means one further step to the unmaking of this world, one more soul destroyed on the pyres. MURDERER, PEICE OF SHIT, SACRIFICIAL IDIOT, EMPTY FUCK; FUTURE OF FIRE AND ASH WILL COME, AND I GIVE YOU ONE HOLY CREED: KILL EVERYTHING THAT ISN'T US."
